      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Summed up in a few words, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Young Souls ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "is just pure fun. A beautiful art style highlights a fast and challenging combat experience, culminating into a game well worth your time. It tells a story of two kids fighting for who they care for most, stacked up against impossible odds. Funny dialogue, well written characters, and personality through character design only serve to further the quality of this game. With only a few, very minor nitpicks weighing it down, I firmly believe ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Young Souls",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is well worth the price of admission.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
